race.description: Ladbrokes Summer Sprint Series Heat 3 Hcp (Bm69)
race.comment: Competitive. FORMS OF FEAR (3) led and won a 70 and then came back in trip in a 76 and couldn't pick up. This suits better and stripping fitter he can bounce back. CROWN WATERS (8) comes out of the same race where he missed a whisker. He will be fitter again and has more up the sleeve. STRUCK GOLD (5)  was quickly back to form easily winning a 70 over 1200m. Maps well and Todd is reunited. A winning chance. VIERI (7) has to come back from a mile and has been kept on the fresh side. The claim 2kg is handy and he is 2/2 here over this trip. Has to be considered. TIME TO BACA (9) is going well and gets in light with the 3kg claim. An outside gate makes it tough for her.
